### Test ChaloAuto API Endpoints
# Install the "REST Client" extension in VS Code to click the "Send Request" buttons below.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api

### 0. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ----------------------------------------------------
### AUTH ENDPOINTS (TESTING LOGIN)
### ----------------------------------------------------

### A. Request OTP (Using Test Passenger Number)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/request-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "+918888000001"
}

### B. Verify OTP (Using Fixed Test OTP: 123456)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "+918888000001",
  "otp": "123456"
}

### ----------------------------------------------------
### RIDE ENDPOINTS
### ----------------------------------------------------

### 1. Find Nearest Route Point
POST {{baseUrl}}/rides/find-nearest-route
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "passengerLat": 28.7041,
  "passengerLng": 77.1025
}

### 2. Request a Ride
POST {{baseUrl}}/rides/request
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "passengerId": "cm0a5test0000test00000001",
  "pickupLat": 28.7041,
  "pickupLng": 77.1025
}

### 3. Accept a Ride
POST {{baseUrl}}/rides/accept
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rideId": "cm0a5test0000test00000002",
  "driverId": "cm0a5test0000test00000003"
}

### 4. Complete a Ride
POST {{baseUrl}}/rides/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rideId": "cm0a5test0000test00000002"
}

### 5. Cancel a Ride
POST {{baseUrl}}/rides/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rideId": "cm0a5test0000test00000002"
}

### 6. Get Ride Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/rides/cm0a5test0000test00000002/status

### 7. Get Ride Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/rides/cm0a5test0000test00000002/details

### ----------------------------------------------------
### PASSENGER RIDE QUERIES
### ----------------------------------------------------

### 8. Passenger History
GET {{baseUrl}}/rides/passenger/cm0a5test0000test00000001/history

### 9. All Rides for a Passenger
GET {{baseUrl}}/rides/passenger/cm0a5test0000test00000001/all

### 10. Current Active Rides for Passenger
GET {{baseUrl}}/rides/passenger/cm0a5test0000test00000001/current

### ----------------------------------------------------
### DRIVER RIDE QUERIES & ACTIONS
### ----------------------------------------------------

### 11. All Rides for a Driver
GET {{baseUrl}}/rides/driver/cm0a5test0000test00000003/all

### 12. Update Driver Availability
POST {{baseUrl}}/rides/driver/availability
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "driverId": "cm0a5test0000test00000003",
  "isAvailable": true
}

### 13. Update Driver Location
POST {{baseUrl}}/rides/driver/location
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "driverId": "cm0a5test0000test00000003",
  "lat": 28.7045,
  "lng": 77.1030
}
